title: 5 challengers to S.F. mayor push grassroots democracy
text:
Photo: Mathew Sumner, Special To The Chronicle Courtney Riddle holds a sign after a San Francisco mayoral candidate public Q & A held by the League of Women Voters. Courtney Riddle holds a sign after a San Francisco mayoral...
The five candidates challenging Mayor Ed Lee in next month’s election include a tech worker, a musician and a retired hospital administrator. They range in age from their mid-30s to mid-60s.
